254
00:25:34,000 --> 00:25:37,400
Apa yang kalian katakan?

255
00:25:39,640 --> 00:25:40,640
Tidurlah.

256
00:26:05,240 --> 00:26:08,120
Bos, opini publik sudah reda.

257
00:26:10,080 --> 00:26:13,480
