mungkin harus menunggu lama.

429
00:37:44,760 --> 00:37:45,640
Kau…

430
00:37:45,760 --> 00:37:47,120
Pulanglah dan ambilkan aku cuka!

431
00:37:47,280 --> 00:37:49,080
Mau numpang makan
dan masih banyak bicara.

432
00:37:49,240 --> 00:37:50,000
Pergi.

433
00:38:04,440 --> 00:38:05,920
Kenapa tak dibalas?

434
00:38:10,200 --> 00:38:11,120
Aku datang.

435
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:13,320
Cepat juga, ya.

436
00:38:15,080 --> 00:38:15,920
Kau?

437
00:38:16,880 --> 00:38:21,000
